OL,3,CLord of the Rings cast pay tribute to
OL,4,CBernard Hill
OL,6,FElijah Wood, Billy Boyd, Dominic
OL,7,FMonaghan and Sean Astin, who play four
OL,8,FHobbits in the trilogy, have paid
OL,9,Ftribute to Bernard at the event where
OL,10,Fthey were headlining.
OL,12,FSean, who plays Samwise Gamgee, began
OL,13,Fby saying: "We love him. He was
OL,14,Fintrepid, he was funny he gruff, he
OL,15,Fwas irascible, he was beautiful."
OL,17,FEchoing Sean's words, Billy Boyd, who
OL,18,Fplays Pippin, said: "We were watching
OL,19,Fthe movies and I said to Dom, I don't
OL,20,Fthink anyone spoke Tolkien's words as
OL,21,Fgreat as Bernard did.
