OL,6,F"He would break my heart. He will be
OL,7,Fsolely missed."
OL,9,FBernard played Captain Edward Smith in
OL,10,Fthe Oscar-winning 1997 epic romance
OL,11,FTitanic, which starred Leonardo
OL,12,FDiCaprio and Kate Winslet.
OL,14,FHe also portrayed Theoden, King of
OL,15,FRohan, in The trilogy directed by Sir
OL,16,FPeter Jackson.
