OL,3,CLord of the Rings cast pay tribute to
OL,4,CBernard Hill
OL,6,FHill joined the cast for the second
OL,7,Ffilm in the trilogy, 2002's The Two
OL,8,FTowers, which won two Academy Awards
OL,9,Ffor best sound editing and best visual
OL,10,Feffects.
OL,12,FLord of the Rings cosplayers pay
OL,13,Ftribute to Bernard Hill at Liverpool
OL,14,FComic Con, the event he was due to
OL,15,Fattend as a guest.
OL,17,FHe returned to the franchise for
OL,18,F2003's The Return Of The King, which
OL,19,Fpicked up 11 Oscars, including best
OL,20,Fpicture and best director for Sir
OL,21,FPeter.
