OL,3,CLord of the Rings cast pay tribute to
OL,4,CBernard Hill
OL,6,FHill first made a name for himself as
OL,7,FYosser Hughes in Alan Bleasdale's Boys
OL,8,FFrom The Blackstuff, which aired in
OL,9,F1982 about five unemployed men.
OL,11,FThe role earned him a Bafta TV
OL,12,Fnomination in 1983, the same year the
OL,13,Fshow picked up the Bafta for best
OL,14,Fdrama series.
OL,16,FPaying tribute, Comic Con Liverpool
OL,17,Fsaid: "We're heartbroken to hear the
OL,18,Fnews of Bernard Hill's passing. A
OL,19,Fgreat loss.
